div.div:
Newsfeed Service
- Uses persistent connection w/ client
to allow server push (long polling, SSE,
or websockets)
- When post service adds new post,
Newsfeed service checks with User service
which users follow the author, and Newsfeed
service updates their newsfeeds in DB
- When user requests their newsfeed,
it's already generated in DB and can be simply
queried by their userId
- When User service adds new followee,
Newsfeed service requests followee's posts from
Post service and merges them into user's
newsfeed
- Could store X posts in newsfeed at any given time,
when user requests the last page, we can asynchronously
add more posts to the bottom of the newsfeed, in
anticipation of the user requesting more
- Partition by userId
